ActCanadian Centre for Management Development Act
PrecisAppointment of JANICE COCHRANE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Principal of the Canadian Centre for Management Development, to be styled President of the Canadian Centre for Management Development, to hold office during pleasure for a term of five years, effective June 16, 2003.
